        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Canva's built-in social scheduler lets you publish designed posts directly from the Canva interface — no export, no re-upload. Thousands of platform-specific templates. Brand Kit ensures consistent colors and fonts. Included with Canva Pro ($15/mo). The scheduler is basic — no optimal timing, no recycling, no inbox. But if you're already in Canva every day, it removes one step from the workflow.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Design and publish from one interface — no export needed</h4><p>Removes the friction of exporting a designed graphic and re-uploading it to a scheduler.</p></div></li>
