          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Included with Canva Pro — no extra cost</h4><p>If you're already paying $15/mo for Canva Pro, the scheduler costs you nothing additional.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: basic scheduling only</h4><p>No optimal timing suggestions, no analytics, no content recycling, no social listening. It's a publisher, not a strategy tool.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

