        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Circleboom combines profile management with scheduling. Fake follower detection, account cleanup, AI post generation, and content curation from industry sources — alongside scheduling across 5 platforms. Not as strong as Buffer or Publer for pure scheduling, and the AI quality is lower than competitors. But for a small business that wants to clean up their follower list and keep their feed active at $24/mo, Circleboom covers both.</p>
